signup landing page, use bulma for now

issue.title: plugin: the WAE microdata parser shouldn't rely on plain json-ld
issue.body: it's up to the webmaster how she defines microdata in markup, can be header meta or inline attrs. The lib can them all, I think, so don't restrict yourself to the json repr. in the end

issue.title: build a demo, alone standing "event" page
issue.body:
to demo that we can RSVP on anything. A page should just display some "event", add schema.org. 100% static, can be ugly.

- host of fission or netlify or zeit
- you CAN add a page here: https://github.com/cod1ng-earth/ce-website
- use "meet at TXB terrace tonight at 6pm"

issue.title: make a plugin "interface"
issue.body: Replace the plugin's green button popup with sth meaningful "add / subscribe" to this event

issue.title: evaluate FOAM to display a map for all events around you
issue.body: no idea if that would work. Besides, search for all events in a city ("Berlin")

issue.body: you'll get forwarded here by the plugin

issue.title: event-wallet: build "my tickets" page
issue.body: show all events in an overview, use the gql result for it
